{
  "stem": "6989.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She would bring us food and push it under that one single plank or board or whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she would send in food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember being hungry, because food was never, like, I don't remember what I ate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's funny.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite big,",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite big.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very big.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I remember that we were sort of on the edge, but there was a lake.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] is a lake?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], yea.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A river.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I remember going to that river.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, to wash laundry--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was like water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For some reason I remember water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Further away from us, quite a bit far, so it was quite large.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, with the immediate near us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never went to any organized activity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hardly remember her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's another thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Dubno ghetto was not that long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe like nine months or so, and then they liquidated it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, two that I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first one I already told you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was when whoever was in the street was killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I do remember a second [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, the Germans were not in the ghetto at all times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What they did was they took some people, young men, and there were gates.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they were, on both sides, gates, like, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had Jewish policeman attend those gates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whenever the Germans came, somebody from somewhere, I don't know who it was, whether they had people on the outside, I do remember that they would warn us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would say, [NON-ENGLISH], they're coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And once they said, they're coming, everybody ran either to hide.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
